==Bundles==
Iridium Bar may be an option in the {{Bundle|dye remixed||y}}.

==Tailoring==
An Iridium Bar is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create an {{name|Shirt151|link=Tailoring{{!}}Iridium Breastplate|class=inline}}. It is an iridium dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the purple dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
*The [[Wizard]] requests an Iridium Bar by mail on the 5th of [[Winter]] (year 2) in the [[Quests#Staff of Power|"Staff of Power" Quest]].  The reward is {{Price|5000}} and 1 [[Friendship]] heart.
*1 Iridium Bar is requested by [[Lava Eel]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 7 to 10.
*[[Fish Shop#Willy's Boat|Willy's Boat]] needs 5 Iridium Bars to repair the anchor.

==Trivia==
*In real life, iridium is a rare silver, brittle metal that can be hazardous in a fine dust and has toxic radioactive isotopes. It is often used to produce hard, durable surfaces for high-precision tools and machine parts. It is the second densest element on the periodic table, being almost twice as dense as lead. 

==History==
{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}
{{History|1.1|Used as a building material to the [[Water Obelisk]] and [[Earth Obelisk]].}}
{{History|1.3.27|Used as an ingredient to the [[Wedding Ring]] recipe.}}
{{History|1.4|Used as a building material to the [[Desert Obelisk]]. Added Iridium Trash can upgrade. Can now be used in [[Tailoring]]. Can be requested in Lava Eel Fish Pond quest.}}
{{History|1.5|Used as a building material to the Island Obelisk and as an ingredient to the Deluxe Fertilizer and Hopper recipes.}}

